r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 Mourinho mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU chu y Inter Milan mua Gareth Bale hinh anh\" title=\"MU ch\u00fa \u00fd Inter Milan mua Gareth Bale h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/inter-milan-muon-vuot-mat-mu-vu-sao-bu-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gareth Bale l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Real Madrid nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd cho r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng M.U c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, b\u1edfi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Bale c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Bernabeu. Trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u1edf Champions League, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBale \u0111ang ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Zidane tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed TBN th\u00ec cho r\u1eb1ng gi\u1eefa anh v\u00e0 HLV Zidane \u0111ang xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Real c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay c\u1ef1u sao Tottenham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t M.U v\u1ee5 Bale</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo The Independent, Inter Milan mua Gareth Bale, h\u1ecd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t M.U trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Italia \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm Bale \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"bale\" title=\"bale\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/4/Gareth-Bale-roi-Real-Madrid-tro-lai-nuoc-Anh-o-He-2018-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Inter mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Bale \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i M.U v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, Inter ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 100 tri\u1ec7u euro nh\u01b0 ph\u00eda Real Madrid y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. Ngo\u00e0i ra \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a th\u00e0nh Milan c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Inter d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi \u0111\u1eadm cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, song kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Inter mua Bale th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League n\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi Bernabeu, anh kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0110\u1ee9c, Ph\u00e1p hay Italia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 M.U v\u00e0 Tottenham v\u1eabn chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf ch\u1ed7 h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Los Blancos y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/rio-ferdinand-muon-mu-chieu-mo-sao-real-madrid-172-184095.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Rio Ferdinand mu\u1ed1n M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Bale</strong></span>.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Gareth Bale \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/15354-42556/033100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Gareth Bale \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1146","checkdouble":"184172"},{"date":"15:34 13/04","title":"L\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o FLC Thanh H\u00f3a n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau l\u1eddi t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o c\u1ee7a HLV Mihail?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/11/lanh-dao-flc-thanh-hoa-noi-gi-sau-loi-t