0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Michael Oliver l\u00e0 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd HLV c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong ngh\u1ec1. Anh \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 ki\u00eau ng\u1ea1o, th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh vui v\u1ebb v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n khoan dung v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. M\u1ed9t khi b\u1ea1n \u0111i qu\u00e1 xa, anh \u1ea5y bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf quy\u1ec1n l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Buffon chi trich trong tai Michael Oliver\" title=\"Buffon ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/trong-tai-tang-pen-cho-real-duoc-ca-ngoi-hay-nhat-nuoc-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Real Madrid 1-3 Juventus, c\u1ef1u tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Mark Halsey ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: &ldquo;C\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi d\u00f5i theo tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c m\u00e0 anh \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng anh \u1ea5y qu\u00e1 thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7m c\u00f2i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn, nh\u01b0ng Michael \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u1edf Champions League &ndash; gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 Michael Oliver, nh\u01b0ng anh \u1ea5y qu\u00e1 quen thu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd bi\u1ebft c\u00e1 t\u00ednh v\u00e0 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a anh \u1ea5y. Ngay c\u1ea3 t\u00f4i, m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Michael, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u00ecn ra t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a anh \u1ea5y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c&rdquo; &ndash; Halsey n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. &ldquo;Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u1edf Wembley v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng N\u0103m t\u1edbi (chung k\u1ebft FA Cup).&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/si-va-trong-tai-buffon-bi-dan-anh-giao-huan-184-184123.html\">S\u1ec9 v\u1ea3 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i, Buffon b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e0n anh gi\u00e1o hu\u1ea5n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/chiellini-to-trong-tai-thien-vi-real-184-184076.html\">C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Juventus b\u1ee9c x\u00fac t\u1ed1 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i thi\u00ean v\u1ecb Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/quyet-dinh-tang-penalty-cho-real-madrid-la-chinh-xac-184-184071.html\">Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eb7ng penalty cho Real Madrid l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ong-ta-la-ke-giet-nguoi-mau-lanh-ke-khong-co-trai-tim-184-184070.html\">\u00d4ng ta l\u00e0 k\u1ebb gi\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e1u l\u1ea1nh, k\u1ebb kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 tr\u00e1i tim</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1144","checkdouble":"184170"},{"date":"15:00 13/04","title":"D\u01b0 \u00e2m CSKA Moscow 2-2 Arsenal: L\u1ea1i l\u00e0 anh, Danny Welbeck","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/du-am-cska-moscow-22-arsenal-lai-la-anh-danny-welbeck.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #06924