rcontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Danny Welbeck v\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a CSKA Moscow v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn nh\u1edd chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-1 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. Ch\u00ednh l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Wenger c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n ch\u1ee7 quan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Du am CSKA Moscow vs Arsenal Lai la anh, Danny Welbeck hinh anh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m CSKA Moscow vs Arsenal L\u1ea1i l\u00e0 anh, Danny Welbeck h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/nguoi-hung-danny-welbeck-cho-biet-arsenal-khong-thoai-mai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Danny Welbeck b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u CSKA Moscow vs Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nCh\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 11 ph\u00fat, t\u1eeb ph\u00fat 39 \u0111\u1ebfn 50, Fedor Chalov v\u00e0 Kirill Nababkin ghi li\u1ec1n 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2-0. \u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng \u00edt ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1ea7n k\u1ef3 gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 AS Roma tr\u01b0\u1edbc Barca hay ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Juventus tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real t\u1ea1i Champions League.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n nh\u1eadn th\u00eam 1 b\u00e0n thua n\u1eefa Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t may \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra. Danny Welbeck ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00fap NHM Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tra t\u1ea5n v\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd k\u00e9o d\u00e0i su\u1ed1t 74 ph\u00fat.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00fat 75, Welbeck \u0111i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Vasili Berezutski tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ea9y b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 cho Mohamed Elneny. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh r\u1ea5t nhanh x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh Elneny.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Welbeck CSKA 2-2 Arsenal\" title=\"Welbeck CSKA 2-2 Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/CSKA-2-2-Arsenal-Khi-Arsene-Wenger-nghi-qua-nhieu-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Welbeck \u0111\u01b0a Arsenal v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m g\u1ecdn g\u00e0ng v\u00e0 l\u1ea1nh l\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a s\u1ed1 23 kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u00e1nh s\u1eadp \u00fd ch\u00ed ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 b\u00e0n gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa \u00e1p l\u1ef1c, Arsenal ch\u01a1i thanh tho\u00e1t trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Ramsey \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ebd t\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/ket-qua-cska-moskva-vs-arsenal-tran-dau-tu-ket-europa-league-201718-184-184122.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 CSKA Moscow vs Arsenal</strong></span> gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 6-3 sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00e1o th\u1ee7 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh th\u1ee9 5 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a Europa League sau tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Fulham (2009/2010), Liverpool (2009/2010, 2015/2016), Chelsea (2012/2013) v\u00e0 M.U \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Welbeck ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u CSKA Moscow vs Arsenal, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/du-am-arsenal-32-southampton-ngay-danny-welbeck-cuu-roi-hang-thu-172-183832.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Danny Welbeck c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Southampton</strong></span>. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-2.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Welbeck giup Arsenal thang Southampton 3-2\" title=\"Welbeck giup Arsenal thang Southampton 3-2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/Welbeck-giup-Arsenal-thang-Southampton-3-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Welbeck ghi 5 b\u00e0n trong 5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nSau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Welbeck \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. C\u1ef1u sao M.U l\u00fac n\u00e0y ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin, ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c v\u1ec7 tinh xung quanh.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Southampton, Welbeck k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Iwobi v\u00e0 Aubameyang. Ng\u00f4i sao 28 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o gi\u00fap ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Gabon ghi b\u00e0n. \u0110\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi CSKA Moscow r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay, anh c\u00f9ng Ramsey v\u00e0 Elneny li\u00ean t\u1ee5c khi\u1ebfn khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng trao \u0111\u1ea3o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nWelbeck \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao. 5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t anh ghi 5 b\u00e0n. N\u1ebfu t\u00ednh tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 10 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Welbeck c\u00f3 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u00e1n m\u1ed1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n hai con s\u1ed1 trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i (sau c\u00e1c m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2011/2012 v\u00e0 2013/2014).&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Welbeck lap cu dup truoc Southampton\" title=\"Welbeck lap cu dup truoc Southampton\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-arsenal-32-southampton.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Welbeck b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a Welbeck \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Arsenal, b\u1edfi HLV Wenger c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. Khi m\u00e0 Aubameyang kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Europa League, s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Welbeck c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean c\u1ea5p thi\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t Welbeck ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c sung s\u1ee9c v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u01b0 th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tham v\u1ecdng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o th\u1eb3ng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Welbeck \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/33902-40942/033100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Welbeck \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1143","checkdouble":"184171"},{"date":"17:29 13/04","title":"Nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 gi\u00fap Arsenal tho\u00e1t hi\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc CSKA Moscow","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/13/nhung-yeu-to-giup-arsenal-thoat-hiem-truoc-cska-moscow.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;p