ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do r\u00fat Bale ra ngh\u1ec9 t\u1eeb s\u1edbm</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-real-madrid-vs-juventus-01h45-ngay-124-champions-league-201718-372-184054.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Real Madrid vs Juventus</strong></span> \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Bernabeu, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, anh ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 b\u1ecb thay ra ngh\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 sau 45 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Zinedine Zidane phat bieu ve Gareth Bale - tu ket C1 hinh anh\" title=\"Zinedine Zidane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Gareth Bale - t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft C1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/zidane-giai-thich-ly-do-rut-bale-ra-nghi-o-tran-gap-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Zinedine Zidane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Gareth Bale</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nZinedine Zidane n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Gareth Bale, v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao r\u00fat c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i thi\u1ebfu n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, t\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng di chuy\u1ec3n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat Bale v\u00e0 Camesiro \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o Marco Asensio v\u00e0 Lucas Vazquez, t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cAsensio v\u00e0 Vazquez \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c di chuy\u1ec3n, h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh, ch\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Juventus kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i thay Bale v\u00e0 Camesiro ch\u1ec9 v\u00ec l\u00fd do chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn g\u00ec v\u1edbi h\u1ecd c\u1ea3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Gareth Bale s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Zinedine Zidane chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Bale, \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 thay th\u1ebf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00ec l\u00fd do chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, song b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ednh chuy\u1ec7n r\u1eddi Bernabeu \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gareth Bale trong tran Juventus 0-3 Real Madrid\" title=\"Gareth Bale trong tr\u1eadn Juventus 0-3 Real Madrid\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/Gareth-Bale-roi-Real-Madrid-ra-yeu-sach-moi--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gareth Bale s\u1eafp r\u1eddiReal Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n. Nh\u1eefng m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Zidane kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p Bale ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Los Blancos c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/chuyen-nhuong-real-mua-salah-thay-bale-trong-mua-he-toi-180-181932.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Real quan t\u00e2m Salah</strong></span>, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Liverpool v\u1ec1 thay Bale. Sterling v\u00e0 Hazard c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu. Real ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm cho nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Bale, anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-italia/inter-milan-muon-vuot-mat-mu-vu-sao-bu-real-176-184172.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Inter quan t\u00e2m Bale</strong></span>, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. \u1ede Premier League, M.U v\u00e0 Tottenham c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Gareth Bale \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/15354-42556/033100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Gareth Bale \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1141","checkdouble":"184177"},{"date":"15:17 13/04","title":"Gi\u1eefa Salah v\u00e0 De Bruyne, Frank Lampard ch\u1ecdn ai?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/giua-salah-va-de-bruyne-frank-lampard-chon-ai.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weig