        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuba Akpom phat bieu ve Jack Wilshere hinh anh\" title=\"Chuba Akpom ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jack Wilshere h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/16/Chuba-Akpom-phat-bieu-ve-Jack-Wilshere-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chuba Akpom khen ng\u1ee3i Wilshere\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nChuba Akpom n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Jack Wilshere, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ebfn nay: \u201c\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, Wilshere l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t m\u1ecdi th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u1eeb h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Arsenal, anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Arsenal, anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp v\u00e0o \u0110T Anh t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm. Wilshere l\u00e0 th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 trong nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChuba Akpom kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf s\u00e2n Emirates, anh b\u1ecb cho r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 \u0111ang \u0111\u00e1 cho Sint-Truiden theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 anh \u0111\u00e1 cho Brentford, Coventry, Nottingham Forest, Hull City v\u00e0 Brighton c\u0169ng theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Jack Wilshere b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u1ec7n \u0111i hay \u1edf c\u1ee7a Jack Wilshere \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u1eeb b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7, anh quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Emirates \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jack Wilshere\" title=\"Jack Wilshere\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/1/wenger-du-sao-arsenal-o-lai-bang-chieu-doc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Jack Wilshere r\u1eddi Arsenal l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/everton-tu-tin-chieu-mo-sao-arsenal-172-184103.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Everton quan t\u00e2m Wilshere</strong></span>, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Italia v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Wilshere kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/wenger-du-sao-arsenal-o-lai-bang-chieu-doc-172-182812.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>HLV Wenger mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Wilshere \u1edf l\u1ea1i</strong></span>, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Tuy nhi\u00ean, qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1eabn \u0111ang g\u1eb7p b\u1ebf t\u1eafc.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nWilshere kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 ph\u00eda Arsenal ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i n\u1ebfu anh ch\u1ecbu gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Wilshere \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/38094-40942/033100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Wilshere \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1139","checkdouble":"184173"},{"date":"16:18 13/04","title":"Thua li\u1ec3ng xi\u1ec3ng, Jesus y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Man City g\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1eady","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/5/thua-lieng-xieng-jesus-yeu-cau-man-city-guong-day.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weigh