\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i chia tay v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh c\u00fa \u0103n 3 trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang xu\u1ed1ng d\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng phanh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1edfi v\u1eady, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gabriel Jesus \u0111ang l\u00ean d\u00e2y c\u00f3t tinh th\u1ea7n cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 trong th\u1eddi gian s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111ang b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, v\u00e0 cho d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea7m ch\u1eafc ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch trong t\u1ea7m tay, ch\u1eb3ng ai mu\u1ed1n chu\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c k\u00e9o d\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gabriel Jesus trong tr\u1eadn thua Liverpool\" title=\"Man City vs Liverpool Van Dijk va Jesus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/thua-lieng-xieng-jesus-yeu-cau-man-city-guong-day.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gabriel Jesus trong tr\u1eadn thua Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;3 tr\u1eadn thua v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee7y ho\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u1ea9ng cao \u0111\u1ea7u, b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng CLB h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Man City \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi 2 tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City v\u00e0 Man United. Ch\u1eb3ng ai th\u00edch thua tr\u1eadn, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 than v\u00e3n hay ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 b\u1ecf l\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau l\u01b0ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tottenham Hotspurs t\u1ea1i Wembley. V\u00e0 ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft ch\u1eebng, Gabriel Jesus v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn thua b\u1ebd b\u00e0ng n\u1eefa tr\u01b0\u1edbc G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tin t\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 Man City tr\u00ean bongda24h<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-man-city-chi-600-trieu-bang-mua-sam-172-184154.html\">Man City chi &ldquo;ti\u1ec1n t\u1ea5n&rdquo; v\u00e0o chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tien-dao-gabriel-jesus-phat-bieu-ve-man-city-172-184116.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Man City quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i danh ti\u1ebfng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-khong-thay-doi-ke-hoach-mua-sam-sau-tran-thua-liverpool-172-184096.html\">Man City kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm sau tr\u1eadn thua Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articler