-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec3m h\u1ecda Wembley</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Pep Guardila x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Man City v\u1eabn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft, v\u1eabn ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u01b0ng&hellip; v\u1eabn thua. 3 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua, c\u00f3 1 l\u1ea7n h\u1ecd b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, v\u00e0 2 l\u1ea7n b\u1ecb l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n hi\u1ec7p 1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ed1 h\u1eefu trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola, khi h\u1ecd v\u1eabn s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng t\u1eed huy\u1ec7t trong h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u00f3 cu\u1ed1n h\u00fat \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c n\u00e0o. \u0110\u00e0nh r\u1eb1ng, ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1eabn n\u1eb1m trong t\u00fai c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad, nh\u01b0ng nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ec7nh, h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u01b0\u1edbc Spurs v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u00f2 c\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tranh gi\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Harry Kane. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u1ebfu ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. S\u1ef1 tham lam, \u00edch k\u1ef7 c\u1ee7a Kane m\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, n\u00f3i l\u00ean tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a anh, v\u00e0 Tottenham ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd mu\u1ed1n ghi th\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb nay \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Spurs s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Ben Davies v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Man City c\u0169ng thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Fernandinho, l\u00e1 ch\u1eafn n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, sau khi s\u01b0u t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ee7 10 chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a. M\u1ed9t Man City tan n\u00e1t v\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9, tinh th\u1ea7n v\u00e0 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pochettino tr\u1ea3 m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 thua 1-4.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Truoc vong 34 Premier League 201718 Dia nguc chua dut hinh anh\" title=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 34 Premier League 201718 \u0110\u1ecba ng\u1ee5c ch\u01b0a d\u1ee9t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/Truoc-vong-34-Premier-League-201718-Dia-nguc-chua-dut-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man City \u0111ang c\u00f3 tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&ldquo;Th\u00e1nh Salah&rdquo; ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mohamed Salah \u0111ang chi\u1ebfm m\u1ecdi ti\u00eau \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 Champions League v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u00ean c\u1ea3 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi th\u1eddi gian v\u1eeba qua. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e1ng, v\u00e0 \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh ngay khi t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t. N\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng Man City, Porto \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng ng\u0103n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho Bournemouth?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield \u0111ang l\u00ean r\u1ea5t cao, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u0169ng b\u1ea3o to\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Ch\u1ec9 thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng (Gomez, Klavan, Matip, Lallana, Can), Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm Bournemouth v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thanh Salah\" title=\"Th\u00e1nh Salah\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/salah.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u00e1nh Salah \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng ai c\u1ea3n n\u1ed5i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t CLB kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu phong \u0111\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, Man United c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n CLB b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng West Brom. M\u1edbi tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y ti\u1ebfng vang l\u1edbn khi l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc &ldquo;nh\u00e0 vua&rdquo; Man City trong t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2 b\u00e0n. M\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 gi\u1eefa 2 ng\u00f4i sao Paul Pogba &ndash; Alexis Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Romero, to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man United \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang sung s\u1ee9c. X\u00e9t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jose Mourinho \u0111\u1ec1u h\u01a1n West Brom &ndash; CLB ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. T\u1ea1i Old Traffford, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City vs MU 2-3\" title=\"Man City vs MU 2-3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/Derby-Man-City-2-3-MU-Don-gian-hom-nay,-Manchester-mau-do!-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n West Brom tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00e0nh London g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00ednh c\u1ea3 Tottenham ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Man City \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i gia th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u1ec1u g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 34 Premier League 2017/18. Chelsea s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u01b0\u1edbc Southamton v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n r\u1ec7u r\u00e3, v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec3m. The Blues g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn d\u1ef1 Europa League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau, v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u g\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1eady sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a West Ham tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Conte \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, The Blues nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd xoay tua l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho FA Cup. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trong m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chicharito go hoa trong tran Chelsea vs West Ham 1-1\" title=\"Chicharito g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a trong tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs West Ham 1-1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/Chelsea-kho-vao-top-4,-Hazard-van-lac-quan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1eady?</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Arsenal, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Wenger \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua chu\u1ed7i phong \u0111\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd Danny Welbeck. Europa League \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi t\u00ean Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 trong 4 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Arsenal \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng Mkhitaryan, Ramsey c\u00f9ng Xhaka. Chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u01b0\u1edbc Newcastle, v\u00ec v\u1eady \u1ea9n ch\u1ee9a hi\u1ec3m h\u1ecda kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lich thi dau vong 34 Premier League 2017/18\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 34 Premier League 2017/18\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/pre.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 34 Premier League 2017/18</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tin t\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 Premier League tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 34</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thua-lieng-xieng-jesus-yeu-cau-man-city-guong-day-172-184176.html\">Thua li\u1ec3ng xi\u1ec3ng, Jesus y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Man City g\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1eady</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/giua-salah-va-de-bruyne-frank-lampard-chon-ai-172-184169.html\">Gi\u1eefa Salah v\u00e0 De Bruyne, Frank Lampard ch\u1ecdn ai?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/morata-bao-chua-cho-mua-giai-te-hai-o-chelsea-172-184151.html\">Morata b\u00e0o ch\u1eefa cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-tien-courtois-bo-chelsea-toi-psg-172-184149.html\">V\u00ec ti\u1ec1n, Courtois b\u1ecf Chelsea t\u1edbi PSG?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pogba-la-thien-tai-ngoai-hanh-tinh-nhung-172-184125.html\">Pogba l\u00e0 thi\u00ean t\u00e0i ngo\u00e0i h\u00e0nh tinh, nh\u01b0ng&hellip;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cong-dong-mang-thi-nhau-troll-viec-harry-kane-doi-ban-thang-172-184088.html\">C\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ea1ng thi nhau troll vi\u1ec7c Harry Kane \u0111\u00f2i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1137","checkdouble":"184178"},{"date":"13:54 13/04","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh 17h00 ng\u00e0y 13/4 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/truc-tiep-khanh-hoa-vs-quang-ninh-17h00-ngay-134-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@fo