b0\u1eddi Romania c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00edch danh nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thay tro HLV Mihail to cao nguoc nhau sau chuoi tran te hai hinh anh\" title=\"Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Mihail t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o ng\u01b0\u1ee3c nhau sau chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/22/hlv-flc-thanh-hoa-bat-ngo-tuyen-bo-tu-chuc-sau-that-bai-thu-2-o-vleague.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Mihail t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o b\u1ecb c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 FLC Thanh H\u00f3a 't\u1ea1o ph\u1ea3n'</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ef1 \u00fd ra ngo\u00e0i \u0103n u\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng xin ph\u00e9p t\u00f4i g\u1ed3m Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh, Nguy\u1ec5n Tr\u1ecdng Ho\u00e0ng, \u0110inh Ti\u1ebfn Th\u00e0nh, Nguy\u1ec5n Xu\u00e2n Th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 Van Bakel. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 h\u1ecfi l\u1ea1i anh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 g\u00ec. L\u00fac \u0111\u1ea5y, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft m\u1ed9t nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea9y t\u00f4i kh\u1ecfi FLC Thanh H\u00f3a. H\u1ecd \u0111i qua nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Bakel l\u00e0 ch\u00e0o t\u00f4i, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0m ng\u01a1.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e1, l\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ee5c n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 th\u00ec \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u c\u0169ng c\u00f3, \u1edf Anh, T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng v\u1eady. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u, l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1ed7 m\u00e3ng, h\u00e0nh x\u1eed thi\u1ebfu t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng nhau nh\u01b0 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Thanh H\u00f3a. T\u00f4i \u1edf \u1ea2-r\u1eadp 10 n\u0103m, nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng v\u0103n minh nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2u c\u00f3 t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 th\u1ebf\", HLV Mihail t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a.</p>\r\n<h2><strong>C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 FLC Thanh H\u00f3a n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi b\u1ecb HLV Mihail t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o 't\u1ea1o ph\u1ea3n'?</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y c\u0169, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110inh Ti\u1ebfn Th\u00e0nh r\u1ea5t b\u1ee9c x\u00fac: \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00e3i nhau tay \u0111\u00f4i tr\u00ean b\u00e1o ch\u00ed. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n so \u0111o v\u1edbi \u00f4ng \u1ea5y v\u00ec ai c\u0169ng hi\u1ec3u \u00f4ng Mihail l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh (giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 1 - PV), t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi ai. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 cho t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1 20 ph\u00fat r\u1ed3i thay ra. B\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u00f4ng \u1ea5y n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 sai s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt. N\u00f3i l\u1ea1i th\u00ec r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi. T\u00f4i n\u00f3i ch\u1eafc g\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 tin\u201d.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfn Th\u00e0nh t\u1eebng l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Thanh H\u00f3a v\u1edbi 23 tr\u1eadn ra s\u00e2n \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Tuy nhi\u00ean anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Mihail tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay. L\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/dtqg-c292-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span> m\u1edbi c\u00f3 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 2 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague-c291-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">V-League</span>. Anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t ph\u00fat n\u00e0o trong to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch AFC Champions League v\u00e0 AFC Cup c\u1ee7a Thanh H\u00f3a.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThanh Long (TTVN)</p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1135","checkdouble":"184167"},{"date":"12:03 13/04","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m danh 4 CLB v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League: \u00d4ng Vua v\u00e0 th\u1eb1ng li\u1ec1u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/diem-danh-4-clb-vao-ban-ket-champions-league-ong-vua-va-thang-lieu.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color