er:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div>V\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au-c184-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Champions League</span>. 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Real Madrid, Bayern Munich, Liverpool v\u00e0 \u1ea9n s\u1ed1 th\u00fa v\u1ecb mang t\u00ean AS Roma.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18\" title=\"V\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League 201718 \u00d4ng Vua v\u00e0 th\u1eb1ng li\u1ec1u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/champions.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><strong><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Roma-57.html\" target=\"_blank\">Roma</span> &ndash; k\u1ebb th\u00edch g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd<br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong> </strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 con m\u1ed3i ngon \u0103n ngay t\u1eeb khi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng Champions League kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, AS Roma l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u00edt nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 ai c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n g\u1eb7p (c\u00f9ng Besiktas). C\u0169ng b\u1edfi v\u00ec m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i gia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng su\u00f4n s\u1ebb, v\u00e0 v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 m\u1ed7i b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ed1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Shakhtar Donetsk \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, Roma khi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3&hellip; &ldquo;ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i&rdquo; khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eb7p. <strong>M\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00ean trung b\u00ecnh v\u00e0 &ldquo;\u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec3m qua m\u00f4n&rdquo;</strong>. H\u1ecd thua 1-2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u1eafng l\u1ea1i 1-0 \u1edf Olimpico v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, Edin Dzeko v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i &ldquo;qu\u00e1 \u0111en&rdquo; khi v\u1ed3 ph\u1ea3i Barca, \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean s\u1ed1 1 cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thua tan n\u00e1t t\u1ea1i Camp Nou 1-4 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 De Rossi c\u00f9ng Manolas \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebfu cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, ch\u1eb3ng ai tin v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1. Tuy nhi\u00ean, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/thay-gi-sau-man-nguoc-dong-khong-tuong-cua-roma-truoc-barca-184-183976.html\" target=\"_blank\">AS Roma \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9ng</span> v\u1edbi l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t 1, 2 r\u1ed3i 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, qua \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1 t\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 v\u0129nh h\u1eb1ng, l\u00e1ch qua khe c\u1eeda h\u1eb9p v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i gia c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Di Francesco v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t. Nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn trong to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e2u? \u0110\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t k\u1ebb th\u00edch t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ea5t, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng <strong>Roma s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i d\u00e8 ch\u1eebng.</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"AS Roma b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18\" title=\"AS Roma b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/c1roma.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>AS Roma t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><strong><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Liverpool-2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool</span> &ndash; Tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i h\u01a1n x\u01b0a<br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong> </strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1i ng\u00e0y Liverpool l\u00e0m vua ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e2u l\u1eafm r\u1ed3i (2004/05). Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1ecd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng 10 n\u0103m. D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Jurgen Klopp, L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft Europa League, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i thua tan n\u00e1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sevilla, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u1ecd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf Cup ch\u00e2u \u00c2u sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc sang m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u00e0 s\u00e1ng su\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, khi \u00f4ng \u0111em v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Mohamed Salah t\u1eeb AS Roma, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u1edf tr\u00ean. C\u1ea3 2 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhau m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o, khi Liverpool trao cho Salah c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u00e0m l\u1ea1i \u1edf Premier League, c\u00f2n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/liverpool-vs-man-city-duoi-got-giay-vua-ai-cap-172-183545.html\" target=\"_blank\">c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u00f3n qu\u00e0 v\u00f4 gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Anfield</span>.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Porto \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Man City trong th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao c\u00f9ng Pep Guardiola \u0111\u1ebfn 2 l\u1ea7n, Liverpool ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1eb3ng ai mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng l\u00e0 CLB d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch ghi b\u00e0n (33 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng) v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 ba Salah &ndash; Firmino &ndash; Mane g\u00f3p t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 23 b\u00e0n. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung Virgil Van Dijk \u0111ang ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, nh\u01b0ng t\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n \u1edf cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a, Liverpool \u0111ang h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ecdi ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec9nh cao. N\u1ebfu h\u1ecd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/cu-cai-da-nay-salah-co-the-gianh-qbv-172-182508.html\" target=\"_blank\">Mohamed Salah c\u0169ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng</span> v\u1edbi 2 &ldquo;qu\u00e1i v\u1eadt&rdquo; Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18\" title=\"Liverpool b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/c1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Man City c\u1ea3 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><strong><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Bayern-Munich-1567.html\" target=\"_blank\">Bayern Munich</span> &ndash; G\u00e3 \u0103n may kh\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1eddng<br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong> </strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc th\u1ee9 2 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League, tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf H\u00f9m x\u00e1m kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-duc/augsburg-14-bayern-munich-hum-xam-chinh-thuc-dang-quang-193-183757.html\" target=\"_blank\">Bayern Munich \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Bundesliga</span>, nh\u01b0ng v\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 6 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp n\u00ean c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n ca ng\u1ee3i qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, Bayern l\u1ea1i g\u1eb7p thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady ch\u01b0a ai ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecb h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t b\u1edfi PSG \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ed3i sinh v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Jupp Heynckes, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Allianz Arena \u0111\u1ec1u g\u1eb7p may m\u1eafn tr\u00ean con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. V\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u, h\u1ecd g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u1ede Anh c\u00f3 4 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kh\u00f3 nh\u1eb1n l\u00e0 Man City, Man United, Liverpool v\u00e0 Tottenham \u0111ang ch\u1edd. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 Barcelona.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng? H\u1ecd v\u1eabn b\u1ed1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c&hellip; Besiktas v\u00e0 qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. \u0110\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng ti\u1ebfp theo, m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa n\u1eef th\u1ea7n may m\u1eafn g\u1ecdi t\u00ean Bayern v\u1edbi l\u00e1 th\u0103m nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng Sevilla. Lewandowski v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, v\u00ec th\u1ebf ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 mu\u1ed1n c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i gia c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u1edfi thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u01b0a h\u1ecd t\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0103n 3, nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh g\u00ec qu\u00e1 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m, \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u1ed1n c\u00f3, <strong>H\u00f9m x\u00e1m v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League.</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bayern Munich l\u00e0 CLB kh\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18\" title=\"Bayern Munich b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/c1bayern.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bayern Munich v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><strong><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Real-Madrid-29.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid</span> &ndash; Nh\u00e0 vua \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c<br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong> </strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean s\u1ed1 1 cho ngai v\u00e0ng l\u00e0 Real Madrid, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. D\u1eaft t\u00fai 2 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng l\u00e0 \u00f4ng vua \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t Cris Ronaldo &ldquo;\u0111i\u00ean cu\u1ed3ng&rdquo; nh\u1ea5t l\u00fac n\u00e0y, v\u1edbi 15 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i, khi Los Blancos th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 l\u00fac nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong Top 4. H\u1ecd hi\u1ebfm khi n\u00e0o gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh qu\u00e1 3 tr\u1eadn, v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-chon-duoc-nguoi-thay-the-zidane-180-179761.html\" target=\"_blank\">Zidane c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i</span>. T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng c\u0169ng thua s\u1ea5p m\u1eb7t Tottenham &ndash; \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 \u00edt kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ea5p CLB.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bu\u00f4ng s\u00fang t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm t\u1ea1i La Liga, Real Madrid ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Champions League, v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 thi. Sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, n\u0103m 2018 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Real Madrid v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh huy ho\u00e0ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. Cris Ronaldo trong 15 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t ghi &ldquo;v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n&rdquo;&hellip; 25 b\u00e0n, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u00e0o c\u00fa hattrick Champions League.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/psg-bi-real-ha-nhuc-qua-den-sao-so-duoc-voi-ken-ken-184-181480.html\" target=\"_blank\">Gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0u m\u1edbi n\u1ed5i PSG</span>, d\u00f9 c\u00f3 l\u00fac b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u, sau \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0a Juventus v\u1ec1 n\u01a1i s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb vua \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, h\u1ecd g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1ebft \u0111i s\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i sau 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng CLB c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng sinh t\u1ed3n m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd nh\u01b0 v\u1eady r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18\" title=\"Real Madrid b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/c1real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real Madrid v\u1eabn v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh cao</h3>\r\n            &nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, 4 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc kh\u00e1c nhau nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec3m chung l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. Ng\u1ef1a \u00f4 Roma, th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi Liverpool, k\u1ebb b\u00ed \u1ea9n Bayern Munich hay \u00f4ng vua Real Madrid, ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao \u1edf ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div>Nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, s\u1ef1 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng, tranh c\u00e3i v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng gi\u1ecdt n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, d\u00f9 g\u00ec ch\u0103ng n\u1eefa &ldquo;phe h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i&rdquo; c\u0169ng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9, c\u00e1c C\u0110V y\u00eau b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ket qua tu ket Champions League 2017/18\" title=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/tu-ket-champions-league-kich-tinh-bat-ngo-va-tran-chung-ket-trong-mo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><br>\r\n</span></span></div>\r\n<table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" style=\"width:100.0%;background:#FFFFCC;border-collapse:collapse;border:none;&#10;    mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-yfti-tbllook:1184;mso-padding-alt:&#10;    0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"1\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100.0%;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;&#10;            mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt\" width=\"100%\" valign=\"top\">\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;            justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Skybet tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o Real Madrid cao nh\u1ea5t cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 3/2 (\u0111\u1eb7t 2 \u0103n 3). Nh\u1eefng t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 Bayern Munich (15/8), Liverpool (3/1) v\u00e0 Roma (10/1)<br>\r\n            <br>\r\n            L\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m v\u00f2ng   b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League v\u00e0 Europa League s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o <strong>5h chi\u1ec1u nay 13/4 (gi\u1edd   Vi\u1ec7t Nam)</strong>, di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Nyon, Th\u1ee5y S\u0129.</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span><br>\r\n            <span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br>\r\n            <span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft   s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o <strong>th\u1ee9 Ba, th\u1ee9 T\u01b0 (r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng 24 v\u00e0 25/4)</strong>, c\u00f2n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 di\u1ec5n ra 1   tu\u1ea7n sau \u0111\u00f3.</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span><br>\r\n            <span style=\"font-s