1a1n song N\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester l\u1ea1i g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool. Sau khi th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i 0-3 t\u1ea1i Anfield, tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Etihad, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/man-city-12-liverpool-song-nho-toc-do-chet-vi-toc-do-184-183994.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Man City v\u1eabn th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool</strong></span>. Qua \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-5.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuyen nhuong Man City chi 600 trieu bang mua sam hinh anh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City chi 600 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua s\u1eafm h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/10/Chuyen-nhuong-Man-City-chi-600-trieu-bang-mua-sam-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Man City d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft UCL</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>H\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u0129 nhi\u00ean, v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Man City mong mu\u1ed1n. H\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean nh\u01b0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/tien-dao-gabriel-jesus-phat-bieu-ve-man-city-172-184116.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Gabriel Jesus \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i</strong></span> \u0111\u1ee9ng l\u00ean sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng xa h\u01a1n, Man City \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean s\u1eb5n k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Th\u00f4ng tin Man City chi 600 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua s\u1eafm trong h\u00e8 2018 m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i tr\u00ean b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh. H\u1ecd t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, m\u1ed9t m\u0169i c\u00f4ng c\u00e1nh v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Guardiola\" title=\"HLV Guardiola\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/chuyen-nhuong-man-city-chi-600-trieu-bang-mua-sam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Guardiola c\u1ee7a <span id=\"ctl00_m_contentBody_sp_title\" class=\"sp_title\">Man City chi 600 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua s\u1eafm h\u00e8 n\u00e0y<br>\r\n            </span></h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chi-445-trieu-bang-man-city-da-co-them-mot-tan-binh-chat-luong-172-179860.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City nh\u1eafm Fred</strong></span> (Shakhtar Donetsk), Julian Weigl (Borussia Dortmund), Jorginho (Napoli) hay Jean-Michel Seri (Nice). H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf Fernandinho l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 t\u1eeb 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng tr\u1edf l\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMan City c\u0169ng d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m cho Thomas Lemar (Monaco), Eden Hazard (Chelsea), Riyad Mahrez (Leicester) v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng tr\u1edf l\u00ean cho m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi. \u1ede khu v\u1ef1c trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, The Citizens nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi Toby Alderweireld, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Tottenham. Ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 600 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap HLV Guardiola tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng m\u1eaft x\u00edch m\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-khong-thay-doi-ke-hoach-mua-sam-sau-tran-thua-liverpool-172-184096.html\">Man City kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm sau tr\u1eadn thua Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/man-city-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-isco-176-183878.html\">Man City c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 Isco</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tiet-lo-raiola-suyt-ban-pogba-sang-man-city-vao-mua-dong-172-183681.html\">Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: Raiola su\u00fdt b\u00e1n Pogba sang Man City v\u00e0o m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/muc-tieu-cua-mu-man-city-xac-nhan-chuyen-toi-premier-league-172-183159.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a MU, Man City x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Premier League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-mua-tien-ve-isco-co-buoc-tien-lon-172-183117.html\">Man City ti\u1ebfn b\u01b0\u1edbc d\u00e0i t\u1edbi ch\u1eef k\u00fd sao b\u1ecb Real b\u1ea1c \u0111\u00e3i</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1131","checkdouble":"184154"},{"date":"09:33 13/04","title":"Th\u00e1i Lan l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 World Cup b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/13/thai-lan-lan-thu-hai-lien-tiep-gianh-ve-tham-du-world-cup-bong-da-nu.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:b