.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Europa League \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra. Tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 CSKA Moscow v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-2. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/ket-qua-cska-moskva-vs-arsenal-tran-dau-tu-ket-europa-league-201718-184-184122.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn CSKA Moscow vs Arsenal </strong></span>gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 6-3 sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsene Wenger phat bieu ve tran CSKA Moscow vs Arsenal hinh anh\" title=\"Arsene Wenger ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn CSKA Moscow vs Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/Arsene-Wenger-phat-bieu-ve-tran-CSKA-Moscow-vs-Arsenal-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>B\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nAtletico Madrid g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi thua 0-1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Sporting Lisbon, song h\u1ecd v\u1eabn gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft l\u00e0 Marseille v\u00e0 Salzburg. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Marseille \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i RB Leipzig 5-3 sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u00ec Salzburg h\u1ea1 Lazio v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 6-5.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/bon-doi-lot-vao-ban-ket-europa-league-ky-tich-tu-ga-nhuoc-tieu-184-184131.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh 4 \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League</strong></span> cho th\u1ea5y Atletico v\u00e0 Arsenal \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 2 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o l\u00fac 17h00 chi\u1ec1u nay (gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam), l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m ph\u00e2n c\u1eb7p v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i tr\u1ee5 s\u1edf c\u1ee7a UEFA \u1edf Nyon (Th\u1ee5y S\u0129).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Wenger ng\u1ea1i Atletico</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Wenger n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn CSKA Moscow vs Arsenal, \u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2. V\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u00f4ng r\u1ea5t ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Atletico \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Arsene Wenger thua nhan Arsenal da mang tam ly chu quan.\" title=\"HLV Arsene Wenger th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 mang t\u00e2m l\u00fd ch\u1ee7 quan.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/hoa-hu-via-cska-moscow-hlv-arsene-wenger-thua-nhan-arsenal-qua-chu-quan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsene Wenger ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn CSKA Moscow vs Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n tr\u00e1nh Atletico Madrid \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, h\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p Atletico \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o NHM c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t mong ch\u1edd \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. N\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, t\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng NHM n\u00e0o b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nWenger h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Arsenal tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ecf ra ch\u1ee7 quan, nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n. T\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi Arsenal c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1128","checkdouble":"184144"},{"date":"10:46 13/04","title":"Bayern \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV thay Jupp Heynckes","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2013/10/jupp-heynckes-vui-mung-sau-khi-tro-thanh-hlv-xuat-sac-nhat-the-gioi.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.clos